Package: birdDistribution
Title: Model Bird Distributions 
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sarah", "Endicott", , "sarah.endicott@canada.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9644-5343")),
    person("David", "Isles", email = "david.isles@ec.gc.ca", role = c("aut")))
Description: Build bird distribution and abundance models in R. The package 
    currently uses INLA to build Bayesian models of bird distribution and 
    abundance in Canada. This is a work in progress.
